# Simple Minds Quiz Application

# Overview

Simple Minds Quiz Application is a Java-based desktop application developed as a semester project for the Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) course. It is built using Java Swing and AWT to provide an interactive quiz experience.

The application allows users to log in, attempt a quiz, answer multiple-choice questions, and view their final score.

# Features

- User Login
- Quiz Rules
- Multiple-Choice Questions
- Countdown Timer
- Automatic Score Calculation
- File-Based Score Storage
- Exception Handling
- User-Friendly Interface

